general_feeling: Since I don't usually wear glasses, I feel a little heavy when I wear them. When I wear them for more than an hour, I have to take them off and take a short break.
challenges: A little heavy, and the lenses are a little blurred.    Take it down briefly and rest my eyes
beh_adapt: When at the supermarket , briefly take it off and hang it on my clothes.
social: Yes. They were curious about what kind of experiment it was about.
improvements: Would it be better to put a strap on head as opposed to glasses. Plus watches and necklaces feel more convenient.
